title: Maybelline XXL Extensions XX-Treme Length Microfiber Mascara 591 Very Black

title: NOORA
description:
NOORA  20ML CPO Swiss Arabian Fragrance - Noora, meaning ' divine light' is a concentrated mukhalat.



It has an oriental  fragrance with rounded off notes which start with soft fruity notes of orange and honey which turns into floral notes of lily, rose and saffron.
 
It has musk, sandalwood, and vanilla notes in the end.


FRAGRANCE NOTES:

  TOP: Orange, Honey
  BODY:Lily, Rose, Saffron
  DRY DOWN:Musk, Sandalwood, Vanilla
